    "description": "▼「铁拳8」是？<br><br>在2025年迎接30周年，全世界累计销售超过5900万套的「铁拳」系列最新作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/dcc9f48bdf4c8a26537723a956d5aed8.poster.avif?t=1770678135\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/dcc9f48bdf4c8a26537723a956d5aed8.webm?t=1770678135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/dcc9f48bdf4c8a26537723a956d5aed8.mp4?t=1770678135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>经由最新硬体打破极限的精细高解析度模组，表现充满个性的32名以上登场角色。新战斗系统「Heat」和在陷入危机时可以发动的超必杀技「Rage Art」，创造出充满爽快感的「互殴」。只要使用新的操作方法「特殊风格」，将可一键享受铁拳独有的刺激策略战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/c558b60d810cf2d635542e2bc8ea9c58.poster.avif?t=1770678135\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/c558b60d810cf2d635542e2bc8ea9c58.webm?t=1770678135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/c558b60d810cf2d635542e2bc8ea9c58.mp4?t=1770678135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>单人游玩模式收录电玩史上延续最久的主线故事，以及深入发掘各角色魅力的角色篇章。另外还有使用照自己喜好制作的人像巡回各地街机，学习战斗技巧的新模式，和在线上可视化大厅与全世界玩家交流及对战等等，具有丰富的游戏模式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/8f8c77e5b2e11bd3c43606255b38ff89.poster.avif?t=1770678135\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/8f8c77e5b2e11bd3c43606255b38ff89.webm?t=1770678135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/8f8c77e5b2e11bd3c43606255b38ff89.mp4?t=1770678135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>另外还有与学习自己或他人游玩风格并进化的AI Ghost的模拟对人战，可以回顾战斗获得建议后再战的重播机能，让玩家展现出最多个性的高自由度角色自订机能等等，让包含等级配对在内的线上对战更有趣的机能也相当丰富。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/80ccde67d4a29904b77b9f62036fd8b0.poster.avif?t=1770678135\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/80ccde67d4a29904b77b9f62036fd8b0.webm?t=1770678135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778820/extras/80ccde67d4a29904b77b9f62036fd8b0.mp4?t=1770678135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
